<NEW>

As WHEELIE moved about the room, TUSCON was getting angry and WINDLORD
left it completely the meeting was getting disrupted.

"Wheelie!" LEO PRIME said from the stage, "Our job is to help. Not
everyone was brought here by choice or for the same reason. Some crash
landed, some traveled here to help with the threat of Unicron and his
minions." He gave WHEELIE and TUSCON a look, "We are all here to
help."

RODIMUS PRIME stepped up behind WHEELIE, or as close as he could get
to the fast moving robot, and if possible laid a friendly hand on his
shoulder. "Calm down, we are all friends here right?" With that last
word RODIMUS looked at TUSCON as well to be sure that he got the point
to cool down on his famous temper.

LEO was on the stage looking sternly across the floor as he gripped
the podium, dealing with anger issues of his own. "This is NOT going
to solve our issues." He glanced at KUP, TUSCON, WHEELIE and a few
others, "Everyone, please retake your seats." He said in a firm voice
in an effort to get the meeting back under control.

Looking over at LORD ELDER, LEO PRIME gestured, "If you would go see
about Windlord?"

ELDER nodded as he got up from his seat walked towards the same exit
of the room that WINDLORD had just used.

(TAG)

Preston
